      <title>Hess 投资者 HBK 将放弃对雪佛龙合并的投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/hess-investor-hbk-to-abstain-in-53-billion-chevron-merger-vote</link>
